text: Ana Paula Rodrigues (born 20 January 1988) is a Brazilian gymnast. She competed in six events at the 2004 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Brazilian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Brazil Category:Gymnasts at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Curitiba Category:Pan American Games medalists in gymnastics Category:Pan American Games bronze medalists for Brazil Category:Gymnasts at the 2003 Pan American Games
